readable.content: A group of five men are standing in the middle of a room that is crumbling and abandoned . A group of guys who appear to be a band stand inside the dark graffiti-covered and rock-strewn building . Five men are standing in a dark room , where there is debris and graffiti on the ground and walls . Five men are standing in a dark room with graffiti on the walls . Four young people are standing in a run down alleyway posing for a picture .
